                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920215-31-off172 t17920215-31-cd173"></join>, one volume of Blair's Sermons, value 1 s. and a variety of wearing apparel
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17920215-31-victim404" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Cooper
